        {
            "title": "特朗普突發威脅 宣布將韓國商品關稅提高至25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普突發威脅 宣布將韓國商品關稅提高至25%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/p6ZB82lPQqbj.JWnvHwuHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/491a1aa0-b53f-11f0-9ffe-dcc228d93c6b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普突發威脅 宣布將韓國商品關稅提高至25%</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
